query:
INSERT INTO agent_activity_logs (id, project_id, task_id, action, reasoning)
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5)
            RETURNING
                id as "id!: Uuid",
                project_id as "project_id!: Uuid",
                task_id as "task_id: Uuid",
                action as "action!: AgentAction",
                reasoning,
                created_at as "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
